RAVDESS Dataset:
How to get the dataset : Register for the dataset at https://smartlaboratory.org/ravdess/

The database has 1440 audio files from 24 actors, each actor with 60 audios The audio files contains 2 statements expressed in 8 different emotions. The name of each audio file in the dataset represents as follows:

Filename Identifiers:

Modality (01 = full-AV, 02 = video-only, 03 = audio-only).
Vocal channel (01 = speech, 02 = song).
Emotion (01 = neutral, 02 = calm, 03 = happy, 04 = sad, 05 = angry, 06 = fearful, 07 = disgust, 08 = surprised).
Emotional intensity (01 = normal, 02 = strong).
NOTE: There is no strong intensity for the ‘neutral’ emotion. Statement (01 = “Kids are talking by the door”, 02 = “Dogs are sitting by the door”).
Repetition (01 = 1st repetition, 02 = 2nd repetition).
Actor (01 to 24. Odd numbered actors are male, even numbered actors are female). 03-01-05-02-01-02-01.wav
